sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as UI
    participant SR as support_routes.py
    participant EH as entry_handler.py
    participant RH as reasoning_handler.py
    participant G as graph
    participant SN as start_node
    participant CN as context_node
    participant IC as intent_class_node
    participant QR as question_readiness_node
    participant RO as routing
    participant RF as response_formatter

    User->>UI: question containing a case ID, no case loaded
    Note over UI: e.g. "What was the root cause of TRM-20230724-0006?"
    UI->>SR: POST /entry/reasoning {case_id: null}
    Note over SR: handle_reasoning_entry() L108
    SR->>SR: _dispatch_entry_handler() L82
    SR->>EH: handle_entry(envelope) L84
    Note over EH: intent == AI_REASONING L67
    EH->>RH: handle_ai_reasoning() L68
    Note over RH: case_id = None L50
    RH->>G: graph.invoke(initial_state) L66

    G->>SN: start_node(state) L6
    SN-->>G: escalated flags = False

    G->>CN: context_node(state) L23
    Note over CN: case_id is None -> skip blob L26
    Note over CN: scan question for TRM-\d{8}-\d{4}
    Note over CN: TRM-20230724-0006 found in question text
    CN-->>G: case_context=None, case_id_in_question=True

    G->>IC: intent_classification_node(state) L11
    Note over IC: case_loaded = False
    Note over IC: llm.with_structured_output(_RawClass)
    IC-->>G: classification{intent, scope, confidence}

    G->>QR: question_readiness_node(state) L18
    Note over QR: case_id_in_question==True L33
    Note over QR: case_loaded==False
    Note over QR: deterministic intercept fires
    QR-->>G: question_ready=False, clarifying=load case message L44

    G->>RO: route_question_readiness() L15
    Note over RO: not question_ready -> NOT_READY L16
    RO-->>G: NOT_READY -> response_formatter
    Note over G: skips router_node + all domain nodes

    G->>RF: response_formatter_node(state) L9
    Note over RF: question_ready=False path
    RF-->>G: final_response{clarifying_question=load case message}

    G-->>RH: graph_result

    Note over RH: question_ready==False L77
    RH->>RH: build_clarifying_question_response() L80
    Note over RH: status=ok L134
    RH-->>SR: EntryResponseEnvelope status=ok

    SR-->>UI: EntryResponseEnvelope status=ok
    Note over UI: question.match(/TRM-\d{8}-\d{4}/i) L2155
    Note over UI: envelope.status==ok and caseIdMatch
    Note over UI: inject Load Case button into output
    UI-->>User: clarifying message + Load TRM-20230724-0006 button
    Note over User: User clicks button
    User->>UI: click Load TRM-20230724-0006
    Note over UI: window.loadCaseById("TRM-20230724-0006") L2278
    UI->>SR: GET /cases/TRM-20230724-0006
    SR-->>UI: case_doc
    Note over UI: hydrateCase(caseDoc) + clearAiConversation()
    UI-->>User: Case Board loaded, AI panel reset
    Note over User: User re-asks question with case now loaded
